lead_paragraph: Atletico Madrid extended their dominance over neighbours Real with a 1-0 derby win on Saturday that leaves the Bernabeu team virtually out of the Liga title race.

headline.print_headline: Atletico Derby Win Virtually Buries Real Madrid
